  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 01ed37436cc08f844852114d42b0854a, type: 2}
    content: "Em ch\u1ECDn m\u1EDF d\u1ECBch v\u1EE5 t\xE2m s\u1EF1, n\xF3 l\xE0
      d\u1ECBch v\u1EE5 (h\xE0ng h\xF3a v\xF4 h\xECnh ), \u0111\xF2i h\u1ECFi k\u1EF9
      n\u0103ng t\xE2m l\xFD ch\u1EE9 kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i xe b\xE1nh m\xEC. H\xE3y
      t\u1EADp trung v\xE0o nh\u1EEFng th\u1EE9 c\xF3 gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng
      cao nh\u1EA5t l\xFAc n\xE0y \u0111i!"
